description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene ('Corynebacterium pseudodiphteriticum'; Bacillus pseudodiphtheriticus; Bacterium pseudodiphtheriticum; Corynebacterium hofmannii; Corynebacterium pseudodiphthericum; Mycobacterium pseudodiphthericum.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
